{"id":842,"parent_id":828,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":842,"title":"Ezekiel 14","subtitle":"","short_title":"Ezek.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/14","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 14"],[".studySummary",["i","The Lord will not answer those who worship false gods and work iniquity—Ezekiel preaches repentance—The people would not be saved though Noah, Daniel, and Job ministered among them."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/14.1","order":"02.27.014.55800"},["b","1"],"Then came certain of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"elders"],"of Israel unto me, and sat before me."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/14.2","order":"02.27.014.55801"},["b","2"],"And the word of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"came unto me, saying,"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/14.3","order":"02.27.014.55802"},["b","3"],"Son of man, these men have set up their idols in their heart, and put the stumblingblock of their",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"iniquity"],"before their face: should I be",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"inquired"],"of at all by",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_3c"},"them"],"?"],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/14.4","order":"02.27.014.55803"},["b","4"],"Therefore speak unto them, and say unto them, Thus saith the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"; Every man of the house of Israel that setteth up his idols in his heart, and putteth the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"stumblingblock"],"of his iniquity before his face, and cometh to the prophet; I the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"will answer him that cometh according to the multitude of his idols;"],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/14.5","order":"02.27.014.55804"},["b","5"],"That I may take the house of Israel in their own heart, because they are all estranged from me through their idols."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/14.6","order":"02.27.014.55805"},["b","6"],"¶Therefore say unto the house of Israel, Thus saith the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"; Repent, and turn",["i","yourselves"],"from your idols; and turn away your faces from all your abominations."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/14.7","order":"02.27.014.55806"},["b","7"],"For every one of the house of Israel, or of the stranger that sojourneth in Israel, which separateth himself from me, and setteth up his idols in his heart, and putteth the stumblingblock of his iniquity before his face, and cometh to a prophet to inquire of him concerning me; I the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"will answer him by myself:"],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/14.8","order":"02.27.014.55807"},["b","8"],"And I will set my",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"face"],"against that man, and will make him a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"sign"],"and a proverb, and I will cut him off from the midst of my people; and ye shall know that I",["i","am"],"the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/14.9","order":"02.27.014.55808"},["b","9"],"And if the prophet be deceived when he hath spoken a thing,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"I"],"the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"have deceived that prophet, and I will stretch out my hand upon him, and will destroy him from the midst of my people Israel."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/14.10","order":"02.27.014.55809"},["b","10"],"And they shall bear the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"punishment"],"of their iniquity: the punishment of the prophet shall be even as the punishment of him that seeketh",["i","unto him;"]],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/14.11","order":"02.27.014.55810"},["b","11"],"That the house of Israel may go no more astray from me, neither be polluted any more with all their transgressions; but that they may be my",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"people"],", and I may be their God, saith the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/14.12","order":"02.27.014.55811"},["b","12"],"¶The word of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"came again to me, saying,"],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/14.13","order":"02.27.014.55812"},["b","13"],"Son of man, when the land sinneth against me by trespassing grievously, then will I stretch out mine hand upon it, and will",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"break"],"the staff of the bread thereof, and will send famine upon it, and will cut off man and beast from it:"],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/14.14","order":"02.27.014.55813"},["b","14"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"Though"],"these three men,",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"Noah"],",",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_14c"},"Daniel"],", and",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_14d"},"Job"],", were in it, they should deliver",["i","but"],"their own souls by their righteousness, saith the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/14.15","order":"02.27.014.55814"},["b","15"],"¶If I cause",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"noisome"],"beasts to pass through the land, and they spoil it, so that it be desolate, that no man may pass through because of the beasts:"],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/14.16","order":"02.27.014.55815"},["b","16"],["i","Though"],"these three men",["i","were"],"in it,",["i","as"],"I live, saith the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],", they shall deliver neither sons nor daughters; they only shall be delivered, but the land shall be desolate."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/14.17","order":"02.27.014.55816"},["b","17"],"¶Or",["i","if"],"I bring a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"sword"],"upon that land, and say, Sword, go through the land; so that I cut off man and beast from it:"],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/14.18","order":"02.27.014.55817"},["b","18"],"Though these three men",["i","were"],"in it,",["i","as"],"I live, saith the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],", they shall deliver neither sons nor daughters, but they only shall be delivered themselves."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/14.19","order":"02.27.014.55818"},["b","19"],"¶Or",["i","if"],"I send a pestilence into that land, and pour out my fury upon it in blood, to cut off from it man and beast:"],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/14.20","order":"02.27.014.55819"},["b","20"],"Though Noah, Daniel, and Job,",["i","were"],"in it,",["i","as"],"I live, saith the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],", they shall deliver neither son nor daughter; they shall",["i","but"],"deliver their own souls by their righteousness."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/14.21","order":"02.27.014.55820"},["b","21"],"For thus saith the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"; How much more when I send my four sore judgments upon Jerusalem, the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"sword"],", and the famine, and the noisome beast, and the pestilence, to cut off from it man and beast?"],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/14.22","order":"02.27.014.55821"},["b","22"],"¶Yet, behold, therein shall be left a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"remnant"],"that shall be brought forth,",["i","both"],"sons and daughters: behold, they shall come forth unto you, and ye shall see their way and their doings: and ye shall be comforted concerning the evil that I have brought upon Jerusalem,",["i","even"],"concerning all that I have brought upon it."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/14.23","order":"02.27.014.55822"},["b","23"],"And they shall comfort you, when ye see their ways and their doings: and ye shall know that I have not done without cause all that I have done in it, saith the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/14.1a","order":"02.27.014.55823"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/8.1"},"Ezek. 8:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/14.3a","order":"02.27.014.55825"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/wickedness"},"TG Wickedness"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/14.3b","order":"02.27.014.55827"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/20.3"},"Ezek. 20:3"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/36.37"},"36:37"],"."],["div",{"id":"3c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/14.3c","order":"02.27.014.55829"},["b","3c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/3.13"},"2 Kgs. 3:13"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-cor/6.14.14-16"},"2 Cor. 6:14 (14–16)"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/14.4a","order":"02.27.014.55831"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/3.20"},"Ezek. 3:20"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/26.20"},"2 Ne. 26:20"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/14.8a","order":"02.27.014.55833"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/17.10"},"Lev. 17:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/14.8b","order":"02.27.014.55835"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/num/26.10"},"Num. 26:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/14.9a","order":"02.27.014.55837"},["b","9a"],["span.small","JST"],"Ezek. 14:9 … I the Lord have",["i","not"],"deceived …"],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/14.10a","order":"02.27.014.55839"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/punish"},"TG Punish"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/14.11a","order":"02.27.014.55841"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-mission-of"},"TG Israel, Mission of"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/14.13a","order":"02.27.014.55843"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/26.26"},"Lev. 26:26"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/14.14a","order":"02.27.014.55845"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/15.1"},"Jer. 15:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"14b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/14.14b","order":"02.27.014.55847"},["b","14b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/6.9"},"Gen. 6:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"14c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/14.14c","order":"02.27.014.55849"},["b","14c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/28.3"},"Ezek. 28:3"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/dan/9.22.22-23"},"Dan. 9:22 (22–23)"],"."],["div",{"id":"14d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/14.14d","order":"02.27.014.55851"},["b","14d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/job/1.1"},"Job 1:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/14.15a","order":"02.27.014.55853"},["b","15a"],["span.small","HEB"],"wild or evil."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/14.17a","order":"02.27.014.55855"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/26.25"},"Lev. 26:25"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/14.21a","order":"02.27.014.55857"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/5.17"},"Ezek. 5:17"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.27"},"33:27"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/6.8"},"Rev. 6:8"],"."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/14.22a","order":"02.27.014.55859"},["b","22a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-remnant-of"},"TG Israel, Remnant of"],"."]]}
